00:00:51.739 --> 00:00:53.379
Trees good.

00:00:53.379 --> 00:00:58.370
Travel to a futuristic world of spaceships,
Mech-Warriors and...

00:00:58.370 --> 00:01:00.489
really crappy wheelchairs?

00:01:00.489 --> 00:01:05.260
Follow along with a team of scientists who
blend in with the natives by wearing the GAP

00:01:05.260 --> 00:01:06.560
